{"tid":2084405,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣2月起入境禁令　往來兩地港人生活計劃被打亂","createTime":"2020-06-29T08:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:31:08.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1de5dd95b7c496634ba880d30f84ac44a519c1f","tid":2084405,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>因應新型肺炎疫情影響，台灣在2月相繼公布有關對大陸及港澳居民入境禁令的措施，打亂了部分港人的原來計劃及生活。</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n嫁到台灣的香港人鳳楠去年中誕下小孩，原本每2至3個月會與香港家人聚會。但受疫情影響，至今已近半年未能返港，她的媽媽非常掛念孫兒，擔心等到再見面時，孫兒已認不到自己。<br />\n<br />\n至於身處香港的Christy，原定今年3月辭職到台灣與男朋友結婚，現因疫情延後婚期之外，也只能靠視訊維繫異地戀情。台灣交通部早前透露，或可能最快於10月重新開放旅客入境，Christy說，屆時會馬上到台灣與男朋友登記結婚和辦理居留手續。<br />\n<br />\n學生方面，在新北市淡江大學就讀四年班的港人Eric，<strong><em>寒假回港過年後便因封關未能趕回台灣，不單無法重返校園，更打亂撰寫論文的進度。</em></strong>他曾聯同其他滯留在港的學生，組成「香港僑生返台關注小組」約見當局反映訴求，現預料7月初能返台繼續學習。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534618-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534618-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=58cd2eb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534618-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30235bb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534618-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"73c97339744f01c2ff1805989364954b48c478a8","tid":2084405,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:24:52.000Z","msg":"一人一post推71<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Facebook Instagram airdrop都要post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n可以一齊轉埋Icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig